{"tid":649463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邨內治安良好　居民：唔知點解咁多休班警員犯案","createTime":"2018-05-01T15:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T06:02:47.000Z","uid":81228,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b88ee81208b94a0b81667429b6e58185329a67","tid":649463,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"一名停職警員昨日凌晨在大埔富善邨的升降機內胸襲年約20歲少女，警方經調查後於今午將他拘捕。事件經報道後，引來區內的市民熱烈討論，又對案件感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n市民張小姐透露，富善邨的治安一向良好，四周都有保安巡邏，平日晚上都會專程經商場回家，不會行經偏僻安靜的地方，而且大廈內有多部升降機，如見到升降機內有可疑男子，寧願選擇乘搭第二部升降機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525096669_a72d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525096669_a72d.jpg&h=3928a978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姚小姐（左）及張小姐（右）均認為邨內治安良好。<br />\n<br />\n她其後表示，今次的被捕犯人為停職警員，認為警方需要正視問題，避免再發生同類型事件，坦言：「唔知點解咁多休班警員犯案，可能佢哋壓力太大」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，住在富善邨的姚小姐表示，大廈內有足夠的閉路電視，加上有保安巡邏，所以覺得治安尚算不錯。她指自己雖不介意與單身男子同乘升降機，但未來與朋友外出後，會叫他們陪同上樓，避免遇到色魔。她續稱，警察作為執法者，不應知法犯法，「唔多唔少會影響對佢哋嘅信任，不過一樣米養百樣人，總會有害群之馬」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180430/58138251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58138251&d=mrVId5AQ4OUmPFqh%2F%2F%2B5IBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5b88ed3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58138251&h=8cf4f839\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180430/58138251</a>"},{"pid":"cd0399e8ecb1d12a74a88d44b51c32253d6f8dd2","tid":649463,"uid":13724,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"一陣會唔會屈條女係港獨份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421d4f11b28b29a56c4dbfe8492eadf967d0d3fc","tid":649463,"uid":127991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"治安好？ 有露體狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c78ece8137621509c3c3d10aa8688e5b64559b","tid":649463,"uid":18167,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"南亞人犯法拉唔到<br />\n內地人犯法唔會拉<br />\n休班警犯法唔會計<br />\n<br />\n呢個香港只有泛民同港獨會被定罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba25c80768fb3280c4a59e7f7bef1b17f93ba651","tid":649463,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"圖入面個2位應該好撚安全"},{"pid":"78d98cce99b31ae9fb173cd278f883cc11af077c","tid":649463,"uid":50727,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba25c80768fb3280c4a59e7f7bef1b17f93ba651","tid":649463,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"圖入面個2位應該好撚安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"吓 張小姐ok喎"},{"pid":"8f49b7486816adf5d44e498a1dcee24e53c16676","tid":649463,"uid":55533,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"78d98cce99b31ae9fb173cd278f883cc11af077c","tid":649463,"uid":50727,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba25c80768fb3280c4a59e7f7bef1b17f93ba651","tid":649463,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"圖入面個2位應該好撚安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"吓 張小姐ok喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/004045_2138196178d7cc917d1668ee75bf2086.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F004045_2138196178d7cc917d1668ee75bf2086.jpg&h=1b50502f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef491c2db57328ae9bee082a43492390bcd41c1","tid":649463,"uid":56698,"l